<p style='margin-top:0cm;margin-right:0cm;margin-bottom:8.0pt;margin-left:0cm;line-height:107%;font-size:15px;font-family:"Calibri",sans-serif;'><strong><span style="font-size:16px;line-height:107%;">1. Aplicaci&oacute;n de los T&eacute;rminos de uso</span></strong></p>
